%% Diagram: Sync vs async publish dispatch in an in-process pub/sub broker
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Pub as Publisher
    participant Bus as Event Bus
    participant A as Sub A<br/>(sync)
    participant B as Sub B<br/>(async)
    participant C as Sub C<br/>(throws)

    Pub->>Bus: publish(topic, data)
    Note over Bus: lookup topic →<br/>ordered Map
    Bus->>A: cb(data)
    A-->>Bus: void
    Bus->>B: cb(data) → Promise
    Bus->>C: cb(data)
    C--xBus: throws
    Note over Bus: per-cb try/catch -<br/>log + continue
    B-->>Bus: resolves later
    Bus-->>Pub: returns true

    Note over Pub,Bus: publishAsync awaits<br/>Promise.allSettled
